-- African Barrick ‘Actively’ Considering West African Acquisitions
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2011-02-09T09:44:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-09/african-barrick-is-very-actively-considering-acquisitions-in-west-africa.html
  African Barrick Gold Ltd . is “very
actively” considering acquisitions in West Africa and the
Arabian peninsula, according to Andrew Wray, head of  investor
relations .  The company wants to diversify its operations and has the
“financial flexibility” to do so, he said in a speech at the
Mining Indaba conference in  Cape Town  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  